data.description: Beautiful four bedroom two bath home.  Nicely updated and cared for.   Walk into a lovely and spacious sitting room adorned with stunning woodwork.  To your left is the spacious and comfy living room that is open to the formal dining room.   The large kitchen has been updated as well as both bathrooms.  Walk up attic is perfect is additional living space is needed.  The possibilities are endless!  Each of the four bedrooms are good size. Close to I-80, schools and shopping!
